WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.230
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:04.150
for joining me again tonight. I really

00:00:04.160 --> 00:00:05.590
appreciate it. I have some things I have

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:08.310
to say really quick. We see these

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:09.910
things that we talked about last night.

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:13.030
Now, last night was very different.

00:00:13.040 --> 00:00:14.870
Everything the Lord showed us in prayer

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:19.910
last night was pretty much

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:23.109
over the top. I believe I saw

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:25.990
Ezekiel, and he was

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.910
standing on

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:30.390
the side of a mountain, and I saw a

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:33.670
valley of desolate dryness.

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:36.470
It was black and white; it wasn't

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:40.150
in color. It

00:00:40.160 --> 00:00:42.630
looked like spiritual warfare.

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:45.990
And as the valley

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.389
was black and white, as I was looking

00:00:48.399 --> 00:00:51.350
into the vision, I could see Ezekiel

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:54.549
standing up with a long robe with holes

00:00:54.559 --> 00:00:58.069
in his gown. It had holes all in it at

00:00:58.079 --> 00:00:59.830
the bottom where it would drag the

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:02.229
rocks,

00:01:02.239 --> 00:01:03.430
because they didn't have pavement back

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:07.510
then. But he had a long

00:01:07.510 --> 00:01:07.520
shofar

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:11.590
in his hands that was a massive horn, and

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:14.390
his beard was clear

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:15.990
down to the middle of his belly in the

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.990
vision,

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:22.070
and it was gray. His hair was

00:01:22.080 --> 00:01:24.710
long; his

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:29.510
facial hair was very thick and

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:34.630
long, like he had

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:35.990
been in the wilderness.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:39.429
As he was

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:42.550
standing there, I saw

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:46.069
light beside him and

00:01:46.079 --> 00:01:48.710
I could see all these clouds.

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:52.389
I heard from a distance with a

00:01:52.399 --> 00:01:57.030
thunderous voice, "Can these bones

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:58.709
live?"And

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:01.350
all of a sudden, he took that

00:02:01.350 --> 00:02:01.360
shofar

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:05.270
and he blew it. It was a

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:08.469
long blast,

00:02:08.469 --> 00:02:08.479
and

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:11.589
it was very beautiful sounding,

00:02:11.599 --> 00:02:15.030
but it echoed the presence of God

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:17.270
through that valley.

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:20.229
The glory of the Lord went through

00:02:20.239 --> 00:02:24.550
that valley, and water started to come

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:28.229
from a massive tree.

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.150
It didn't come from the tree; it

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:31.750
went by the tree,

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:33.030
because there are

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:36.229
scriptures that back this.

00:02:36.239 --> 00:02:39.589
I saw the river of

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:42.550
this water start to flow the moment he

00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:45.830
blew the horn, and it

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:48.309
started going over this cliff of

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:52.470
a beautiful rock.

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:08.630
He was standing,

00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:11.830
then he sat down and took his place

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:15.190
of authority by resting

00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:17.670
at the edge of this rock, and the

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:20.869
water came over and

00:03:20.879 --> 00:03:23.750
he was looking at

00:03:23.750 --> 00:03:23.760
it.

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:26.070
I saw the tree, and it was

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:28.309
one of those large

00:03:28.309 --> 00:03:28.319
sequoia

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:32.630
trees, a massive tree that was

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:35.350
right by the river of water.

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:39.190
As

00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:42.710
I was looking into this, I saw a piece

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:45.990
of fruit that was cut in half.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:48.470
There was a seed in the

00:03:48.480 --> 00:03:50.630
fruit that

00:03:50.630 --> 00:03:50.640
looked

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:53.750
like a peach pit,

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:57.350
covered with blood.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.869
It was covered with the blood of

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:02.309
Jesus. And the Lord was showing us

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:06.309
that all the seeds laid dormant,

00:04:06.319 --> 00:04:10.309
but they're not dead.

00:04:10.319 --> 00:04:13.509
The seeds from the past will have a

00:04:13.519 --> 00:04:15.990
harvest come at last.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.550
I saw the manifestation

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:22.150
of all the seeds we've sowed, whether

00:04:22.150 --> 00:04:22.160
they

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:25.270
be bad or good;

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:27.909
seed time and harvest never ceases.

00:04:27.919 --> 00:04:30.070
The Lord gave us Genesis

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:32.070
8.

00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:34.629
I saw seed time and harvest

00:04:34.639 --> 00:04:36.310
accelerating,

00:04:36.320 --> 00:04:38.950
and I saw the blessing.

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:41.670
The Lord said, "Pray over your past

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:44.790
seeds for a crop

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:47.430
failure."So

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:50.310
we call for a crop failure over our

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:52.629
past seeds so that they don't bear any

00:04:52.639 --> 00:04:54.710
fruit.

00:04:57.840 --> 00:05:00.870
It was absolutely beautiful what I

00:05:00.880 --> 00:05:02.870
was seeing,

00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:05.909
and he gave the scriptures.

00:05:05.919 --> 00:05:12.230
Then I saw a baby in a bassinet stroller

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:15.189
that was braided with gold.

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:16.710
It was a white

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:18.230
bassinet,

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:21.029
and the baby was laying in

00:05:21.029 --> 00:05:21.039
it

00:05:21.039 --> 00:05:23.189
with one of those gowns that you use

00:05:23.189 --> 00:05:23.199
when

00:05:23.199 --> 00:05:25.749
you take them

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:29.590
to get dedicated before the Lord. It was

00:05:29.600 --> 00:05:31.670
a beautiful white gown that was

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:34.070
sparkling with

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:37.110
glitter and glowing,

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:39.430
and I could see the presence of the

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:43.110
Lord on that baby. The feet of the baby

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:45.590
were kicking around,

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:50.310
excited, like it's cooing

00:05:50.310 --> 00:05:50.320
and

00:05:50.320 --> 00:05:53.590
excited about life. I couldn't

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:57.029
see the baby, but I could see the feet.

00:05:57.039 --> 00:06:01.830
Then I saw a man with no face;

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:04.309
it looked like a face

00:06:04.309 --> 00:06:04.319
with

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:07.270
a veil over it. I

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:09.590
couldn't make it out, but he had the

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:14.309
same gown on as the baby did. He was

00:06:14.319 --> 00:06:17.029
looking over in that baby's

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:19.029
bassinet.

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:21.110
You couldn't see what he

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:22.230
was focused on because there were no

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:23.909
eyes, nose,

00:06:23.909 --> 00:06:23.919
or

00:06:23.919 --> 00:06:25.510
mouth, but I could see

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:28.230
his face was toward the baby.

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:36.309
The Lord started talking to us

00:06:36.319 --> 00:06:38.710
about coming as a child,

00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:40.550
that we're God's children.

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:52.629
Then I saw

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:55.590
a fox with a black charcoal nose

00:06:55.590 --> 00:06:55.600
and

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:58.870
eyes.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:01.589
It was a big fox.

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:06.790
The small foxes spoil

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:10.710
the vines, but as I could

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:13.589
see the cliff where the water was coming

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:15.350
down,

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:18.309
I saw this fox looking up at the

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:21.110
water and looking at Ezekiel. It was

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:24.309
staring with a gaze,

00:07:26.960 --> 00:07:28.790
but it didn't do anything.

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:33.909
But as I saw this, I saw a

00:07:33.919 --> 00:07:35.909
pair of lungs

00:07:35.919 --> 00:07:40.150
inside of that waterfall.

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:43.909
The lungs were detached

00:07:43.919 --> 00:07:47.110
from the body,

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:49.270
and

00:07:49.280 --> 00:07:51.830
they were breathing.

00:07:51.840 --> 00:07:54.390
The water was

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.550
filling them up;

00:07:56.550 --> 00:07:56.560
it

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:58.070
was

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:00.469
Holy Spirit. You could see

00:08:00.479 --> 00:08:03.270
the lungs exhale and inhale.

00:08:03.270 --> 00:08:03.280
It

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:07.270
was

00:08:07.270 --> 00:08:07.280
the

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:08.950
living water that was flowing out of

00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:11.510
those lungs. I could see the veins;

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:14.550
I could see the

00:08:16.479 --> 00:08:16.950
trachea.

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:19.990
It was

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:23.029
highlighted in a beautiful

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:25.430
blue.

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:29.430
As I see

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:31.589
these visions, the Lord was showing

00:08:31.599 --> 00:08:34.149
me that scripture from Ezekiel

00:08:44.399 --> 00:08:45.829
47.

00:08:45.839 --> 00:08:49.350
Fruit trees of all kinds

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:53.350
will grow on both banks of the river.

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:57.350
Their leaves will not wither, nor

00:08:57.350 --> 00:08:57.360
will

00:08:57.360 --> 00:08:59.829
their fruit

00:09:01.519 --> 00:09:05.110
fail.

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:08.949
Every month they will bear fruit

00:09:08.959 --> 00:09:12.470
because the water from the sanctuary

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:15.829
flows

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:28.070
to them. Their fruit will serve for food

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:30.070
and their leaves for healing.

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.470
I thought it was cool because

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:39.910
people found that,

00:09:39.920 --> 00:09:42.790
and

00:09:46.880 --> 00:09:51.110
it validates the

00:09:51.110 --> 00:09:51.120
vision

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:54.150
more. You don't want to be flaky.

00:09:59.360 --> 00:10:01.430
He's trying to get a hold of his

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:03.190
body because there's a

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:05.590
