00:10:13.680 --> 00:10:15.910
New York, Las

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:18.630
Vegas, New Orleans,

00:10:18.640 --> 00:10:21.590
Miami,

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:24.230
Nevada, Beverly

00:10:24.230 --> 00:10:24.240
Hills—every

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:26.230
one of these places

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:28.550
that would try to have a terrorist

00:10:28.560 --> 00:10:31.750
