00:30:01.200 --> 00:30:03.830
I took my feet and I said, 'You want

00:30:03.840 --> 00:30:05.990
me to jump?'He said, 'Trust me,

00:30:06.000 --> 00:30:07.669
Brandon.'I

00:30:07.679 --> 00:30:11.350
said, 'Of course,

00:30:11.360 --> 00:30:12.789
Lord.'I

00:30:12.799 --> 00:30:15.830
took my feet and I fell

00:30:15.840 --> 00:30:18.789
inside of that portal.

00:30:18.799 --> 00:30:22.230
It was moving and breathing and I

00:30:22.240 --> 00:30:27.029
was instantaneously taken to my past.

00:30:27.039 --> 00:30:28.710
And I went to the hospital where my

00:30:28.720 --> 00:30:31.750
little girl got her shots.

00:30:31.760 --> 00:30:34.389
And he said, 'Brandon, you've asked me

00:30:34.399 --> 00:30:36.710
and asked me to have the

00:30:36.720 --> 00:30:39.190
opportunity in your

00:30:39.200 --> 00:30:40.789
heart

00:30:40.799 --> 00:30:43.190
to have a second chance to tell

00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:46.549
yourself not to give Megan the

00:30:46.559 --> 00:30:49.110
flu shot.

00:30:49.120 --> 00:30:51.750
I'm going to give you that

00:30:51.750 --> 00:30:51.760
request.'And

00:30:51.760 --> 00:30:54.710
all of a sudden he said,

00:30:54.720 --> 00:30:57.590
'Go now. You're about to do

00:30:57.590 --> 00:30:57.600
it.'I

00:30:57.600 --> 00:31:01.430
ran

00:31:01.430 --> 00:31:01.440
and

00:31:01.440 --> 00:31:03.830
I could see the hospital room. I knew

00:31:03.840 --> 00:31:06.149
it was on the fourth floor.

00:31:06.159 --> 00:31:08.950
I ran all the way up the stairs.

00:31:08.960 --> 00:31:12.070
I busted through the doctor's office

00:31:12.080 --> 00:31:15.830
and I saw the nurse about

00:31:15.840 --> 00:31:20.230
ready to give Megan the vaccination.

00:31:20.240 --> 00:31:24.149
And at me as a young man and my wife

00:31:24.159 --> 00:31:25.669
was sitting there and we were watching

00:31:25.679 --> 00:31:30.149
our daughter about to get this flu shot,

00:31:30.159 --> 00:31:33.830
I said, 'Stop.

00:31:33.840 --> 00:31:35.990
Don't do

00:31:35.990 --> 00:31:36.000
it.'And

00:31:36.000 --> 00:31:38.710
all of a sudden,

00:31:38.720 --> 00:31:40.950
that nurse took that thing back and

00:31:40.960 --> 00:31:43.509
did not administer that and a scream

00:31:43.519 --> 00:31:46.230
came before my face.

00:31:46.240 --> 00:31:50.070
And every single year was planned

00:31:50.080 --> 00:31:52.310
out in front of me from where I was

00:31:52.320 --> 00:31:55.830
to the present. And now this has

00:31:55.840 --> 00:31:57.590
been years ago. And this is just out of

00:31:57.600 --> 00:32:00.789
my memory of everything that happened.

00:32:00.799 --> 00:32:04.549
So if I miss anything, forgive me. But I

00:32:04.559 --> 00:32:07.990
remember I saw it play out and

00:32:08.000 --> 00:32:09.750
Jesus stood right there and he said,

00:32:09.760 --> 00:32:11.590
'Now I want to show you the power of

00:32:11.600 --> 00:32:14.470
a decision.

00:32:14.480 --> 00:32:18.549
Watch what happens now with your life

00:32:18.559 --> 00:32:20.630
because of that vaccination or what

00:32:20.640 --> 00:32:22.789
would change.'Megan was already

00:32:22.799 --> 00:32:24.549
developed. She was already starting to

00:32:24.559 --> 00:32:27.830
talk. She was totally normal. Her

00:32:27.830 --> 00:32:27.840
Apgar

00:32:27.840 --> 00:32:31.269
scores were completely normal.

00:32:31.279 --> 00:32:34.470
But as that did not happen,

00:32:34.480 --> 00:32:38.070
I was a bad person. I was very angry.

00:32:38.080 --> 00:32:40.870
I was very verbally abusive to my wife

00:32:40.880 --> 00:32:43.750
all the time. I talked down to

00:32:43.760 --> 00:32:46.870
her. I didn't treat her right. I was

00:32:46.880 --> 00:32:48.710
very hard-hearted.

00:32:48.720 --> 00:32:50.950
I was very angry at the finances.

00:32:50.960 --> 00:32:53.269
Where we were financially,

00:32:53.279 --> 00:32:56.230
I was very bitter towards a lot of

00:32:56.240 --> 00:32:58.470
things.

00:32:58.480 --> 00:33:02.149
But the moment Megan didn't get that and

00:33:02.159 --> 00:33:05.590
change didn't happen, I saw

00:33:05.600 --> 00:33:09.430
my life without the pressure of autism

00:33:09.440 --> 00:33:11.909
is what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:33:11.919 --> 00:33:15.590
Megan developed

00:33:15.590 --> 00:33:15.600
normally.

00:33:15.600 --> 00:33:18.950
Everything was normal.

00:33:18.960 --> 00:33:21.909
But I didn't change.

00:33:21.919 --> 00:33:25.509
I became even more hard.

00:33:25.519 --> 00:33:28.470
And Diana

00:33:28.480 --> 00:33:31.830
and I drifted

00:33:31.840 --> 00:33:33.750
apart.

00:33:33.760 --> 00:33:38.710
I saw the year that Diana left me and

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:41.830
she moved back home to Texas to be with

00:33:41.840 --> 00:33:45.909
her mama and she filed for a divorce.

00:33:45.919 --> 00:33:47.830
I saw it all play right in front of my

00:33:47.840 --> 00:33:49.909
face in a movie screen of all the power

00:33:49.919 --> 00:33:53.029
of a choice because what didn't

00:33:53.039 --> 00:33:56.470
change me was my daughter's special

00:33:56.480 --> 00:33:58.070
needs.

00:33:58.080 --> 00:34:00.389
I saw it all pan out in front of

00:34:00.399 --> 00:34:01.990
me.

00:34:02.000 --> 00:34:06.789
I saw when Diana left;

00:34:06.799 --> 00:34:09.589
she got remarried to a man that was

00:34:09.599 --> 00:34:12.790
pretty wealthy. I saw Megan on the

00:34:12.800 --> 00:34:14.710
weekends

00:34:14.720 --> 00:34:17.669
every other week.

00:34:17.679 --> 00:34:21.349
I became even more angry.

00:34:21.359 --> 00:34:25.270
Her life was better. Mine wasn't.

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:27.669
I didn't get remarried.

00:34:27.679 --> 00:34:31.109
I was very

00:34:31.109 --> 00:34:31.119
angry—heavier

00:34:31.119 --> 00:34:36.389
than what I am now.

00:34:36.399 --> 00:34:38.470
He said, "I want to show you now: your son

00:34:38.480 --> 00:34:41.109
won't be born and there's a call on his

00:34:41.119 --> 00:34:43.349
life,

00:34:43.359 --> 00:34:45.190
and here in the future you'll have a

00:34:45.200 --> 00:34:47.270
little girl.

00:34:47.280 --> 00:34:49.430
You'll have a little girl, and she won't

00:34:49.440 --> 00:34:52.310
be born either, and she has a major call

00:34:52.320 --> 00:34:55.750
in her life

00:34:55.750 --> 00:34:55.760
too."He

00:34:55.760 --> 00:34:59.910
said,

00:34:59.910 --> 00:34:59.920
"Brandon..."He

00:34:59.920 --> 00:35:01.349
started preaching to me and he

00:35:01.359 --> 00:35:02.710
started talking to me about

00:35:02.710 --> 00:35:02.720
everything—to

00:35:02.720 --> 00:35:04.470
sum it up and not make this really

00:35:04.480 --> 00:35:05.910
long for y'all tonight because I'm

00:35:05.920 --> 00:35:08.230
already going over.

00:35:08.240 --> 00:35:11.670
But he said, "Brandon,

00:35:11.680 --> 00:35:17.589
I didn't cause Megan to have autism.

00:35:17.599 --> 00:35:21.270
I did not

00:35:21.280 --> 00:35:25.829
do this to you to teach you

00:35:25.829 --> 00:35:25.839
anything."He

00:35:25.839 --> 00:35:29.750
said to me,

00:35:29.760 --> 00:35:31.670
"The devil comes to kill, steal, and

00:35:31.680 --> 00:35:37.030
destroy.

00:35:37.040 --> 00:35:40.550
But what the devil meant for bad,

00:35:40.560 --> 00:35:42.230
I'll turn it around for good in your

00:35:42.240 --> 00:35:44.150
favor.

00:35:44.160 --> 00:35:45.910
You're not big enough to mess up your

00:35:45.920 --> 00:35:48.790
life.

00:35:48.800 --> 00:35:50.230
You're not big enough to mess up your

00:35:50.240 --> 00:35:51.990
life, Brandon. No matter how many bad

00:35:52.000 --> 00:35:53.910
choices you've made, he said,

00:35:53.920 --> 00:35:56.710
'As long as the footsteps of the

00:35:56.720 --> 00:36:01.349
righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:36:01.359 --> 00:36:03.349
And as long as you're right with

00:36:03.359 --> 00:36:07.349
me and you're seeking me, I'll turn it

00:36:07.359 --> 00:36:09.109
around.

00:36:09.119 --> 00:36:10.870
I'll turn what the devil meant for bad,

00:36:10.880 --> 00:36:12.150
Brandon, and I'll turn it around for

00:36:12.160 --> 00:36:13.910
good in your favor as long as you're

00:36:13.920 --> 00:36:16.950
looking towards

00:36:16.950 --> 00:36:16.960
me.'"Because

00:36:16.960 --> 00:36:18.950
in my mind, I always told him,

00:36:18.960 --> 00:36:21.270
"I can't do ministry. I can't lay hands

00:36:21.280 --> 00:36:23.030
on the sick. I can't do all that because

00:36:23.030 --> 00:36:23.040
of

00:36:23.040 --> 00:36:26.069
Megan, Lord. What do you call

00:36:26.079 --> 00:36:27.349
me to healing ministry? Well, you

00:36:27.349 --> 00:36:27.359
called

00:36:27.359 --> 00:36:30.230
me to do all these things. I'm

00:36:30.240 --> 00:36:32.150
broken because of this."But he said,

00:36:32.160 --> 00:36:34.150
"Brandon,

00:36:34.160 --> 00:36:37.349
Megan does not validate my word. My word

00:36:37.359 --> 00:36:39.750
validates itself.

00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:41.750
It's a pillar.

00:36:41.760 --> 00:36:44.790
Megan's healing doesn't validate

00:36:44.800 --> 00:36:47.510
that I'm a healer. My word validates

00:36:47.520 --> 00:36:55.750
that."As

00:36:55.760 --> 00:36:59.670
he said all these things to me,

00:36:59.680 --> 00:37:02.870
I saw the pressure

00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:05.990
from having a child with special needs.

00:37:06.000 --> 00:37:09.030
As I was ready to drive off a bridge, as

00:37:09.040 --> 00:37:11.589
I was ready to do away with myself

00:37:11.599 --> 00:37:13.670
so many different times, as I was

00:37:13.680 --> 00:37:16.630
driving home and crying behind the

00:37:16.640 --> 00:37:18.950
toilets, cleaning the church bathrooms,

00:37:18.960 --> 00:37:20.470
and doing all the things that I went

00:37:20.480 --> 00:37:24.150
through being a janitor for 15

00:37:24.150 --> 00:37:24.160
years—it

00:37:24.160 --> 00:37:26.710
molded me.

00:37:26.720 --> 00:37:29.190
It took a really hard heart and made it

00:37:29.200 --> 00:37:31.829
soft as I had to buckle up

00:37:31.839 --> 00:37:34.630
and honor my wife and go

00:37:34.640 --> 00:37:38.150
through this very hard time raising a

00:37:38.160 --> 00:37:41.670
child with special needs. The pressure

00:37:41.680 --> 00:37:43.670
on the potter's wheel makes you

00:37:43.680 --> 00:37:49.750
different if you yield to it.

00:37:49.760 --> 00:37:53.030
It's the pressure.

00:37:53.040 --> 00:37:55.030
We have this treasure in earthen vessels

00:37:55.040 --> 00:37:56.390
that the excellency of the power will be

00:37:56.400 --> 00:37:59.030
known to him and not of us.

00:37:59.040 --> 00:38:04.310
But the pressure

00:38:04.320 --> 00:38:07.109
from Megan and all

00:38:07.119 --> 00:38:09.910
the things that I went through

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:15.349
made me into who I am today.

00:38:15.359 --> 00:38:17.430
As he kept telling me that I couldn't

00:38:17.440 --> 00:38:20.390
mess my life up no matter how bad I've done

00:38:20.400 --> 00:38:23.349
things in the past,

00:38:23.359 --> 00:38:25.349
he said, "I told you if the

00:38:25.359 --> 00:38:27.190
footsteps of the righteous are ordered

00:38:27.190 --> 00:38:27.200
of

00:38:27.200 --> 00:38:32.150
the

00:38:32.150 --> 00:38:32.160
Lord."He

00:38:32.160 --> 00:38:34.150
encouraged me. He preached to me. He

00:38:34.160 --> 00:38:35.990
preached a really fiery message that I

00:38:35.990 --> 00:38:36.000
wish

00:38:36.000 --> 00:38:39.990
I could remember all of it.

00:38:40.000 --> 00:38:43.829
I've never heard Jesus as a preacher.

00:38:43.839 --> 00:38:45.750
And boy, he could preach fire.

00:38:45.760 --> 00:38:49.270
I'll never forget it. I sat

00:38:49.280 --> 00:38:50.790
there and watched him as he

00:38:50.800 --> 00:38:52.470
preached to me, and he told me that I

00:38:52.480 --> 00:38:53.990
had a call on my life and he wanted me

00:38:54.000 --> 00:38:57.910
to do something for him.

00:38:57.920 --> 00:39:00.310
I thought at that moment that I

00:39:00.310 --> 00:39:00.320
had

00:39:00.320 --> 00:39:02.710
totally derailed my life because of

00:39:02.720 --> 00:39:04.390
what the doctor had told us: that Megan

00:39:04.400 --> 00:39:06.630
would never be normal and that she would

00:39:06.640 --> 00:39:08.390
never be potty trained. She would never

00:39:08.400 --> 00:39:12.310
have a normal life, and

00:39:12.310 --> 00:39:12.320
we'd

00:39:12.320 --> 00:39:13.829
be lucky if she ever gets out of

00:39:13.829 --> 00:39:13.839
an

00:39:13.839 --> 00:39:15.670
18-month-old's

00:39:15.670 --> 00:39:15.680
stage.

00:39:15.680 --> 00:39:16.950
But that's why I've tried to tell you

00:39:16.960 --> 00:39:19.670
all over and over again.

00:39:19.680 --> 00:39:22.069
Right now, we weren't able to do

00:39:22.069 --> 00:39:22.079
anything.

00:39:22.079 --> 00:39:23.750
If anybody realized how bad

00:39:23.760 --> 00:39:26.150
Megan was—she would urinate on

00:39:26.160 --> 00:39:27.990
everything. She would play with her

00:39:28.000 --> 00:39:31.109
feces every day. She would

00:39:31.119 --> 00:39:33.670
bite herself until blood would

00:39:33.680 --> 00:39:36.470
run down her hands,

00:39:36.480 --> 00:39:40.390
pull her hair out. She had huge bald

00:39:40.400 --> 00:39:42.310
spots all over her head where she'd pull

00:39:42.320 --> 00:39:46.710
all her hair out,

00:39:48.880 --> 00:39:50.790
take everything out of one drawer in one

00:39:50.800 --> 00:39:52.069
room and put it in there. I never knew

00:39:52.079 --> 00:39:54.710
where my toothbrush was.

00:39:54.720 --> 00:39:57.109
I never knew where my deodorant was. I

00:39:57.119 --> 00:39:58.470
never knew where my soap from my

00:39:58.480 --> 00:39:59.910
bathroom was. She'd take all the

00:39:59.920 --> 00:40:01.750
ornaments off the tree every single year

00:40:01.760 --> 00:40:04.150
and put them in the kitchen sink. We

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:05.910
never could have a Christmas tree. We

00:40:05.920 --> 00:40:08.150
never could do anything.

00:40:08.160 --> 00:40:12.550
We did that for years.

00:40:12.560 --> 00:40:16.950
And then one day Jesus visited us.

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:18.950
And in that time whenever he visited, I

00:40:18.960 --> 00:40:22.150
was at the sink and I was complaining,

00:40:22.160 --> 00:40:23.910
and I said to him, "You don't

00:40:23.920 --> 00:40:26.710
hear anything I'm saying? I prayed and

00:40:26.720 --> 00:40:27.990
prayed and prayed for her to get

00:40:28.000 --> 00:40:29.829
better."And

00:40:29.839 --> 00:40:32.470
I said, "She's not. Do you hear,

00:40:32.480 --> 00:40:34.230
and have you heard, any of my

00:40:34.230 --> 00:40:34.240
prayers?"I

00:40:34.240 --> 00:40:38.630
was washing the dishes.

00:40:38.640 --> 00:40:40.790
And at that time, the glory of the Lord

00:40:40.800 --> 00:40:43.190
filled my whole house. And I saw him

00:40:43.200 --> 00:40:45.510
visibly again.

00:40:45.520 --> 00:40:48.470
I was on the floor and Diana

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:50.390
couldn't see him. I was on the floor

00:40:50.400 --> 00:40:53.990
and he melted me like wax.

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:56.950
I thought I was going to die.

00:40:56.960 --> 00:40:58.550
The presence of the Lord was so strong

00:40:58.560 --> 00:41:00.150
in my house; I thought I was going to

00:41:00.160 --> 00:41:02.309
die.

00:41:03.920 --> 00:41:06.309
I looked up at him and I said, "Jesus,

00:41:06.319 --> 00:41:08.470
don't you know what I've asked

00:41:08.470 --> 00:41:08.480
for?"Because

00:41:08.480 --> 00:41:09.990
he asked me, the first thing he

00:41:10.000 --> 00:41:14.150
asked me was, "What do you have need of?"I said,

00:41:14.150 --> 00:41:14.160
"Don't you know

00:41:14.160 --> 00:41:16.870
what I have need of?

00:41:19.270 --> 00:41:19.280
Megan!"He

00:41:21.200 --> 00:41:23.109
said, "According to your faith, be it

00:41:23.119 --> 00:41:26.630
done unto you, Brandon.

00:41:26.640 --> 00:41:28.470
According to your faith, be it done unto

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:31.109
you."Diana

00:41:31.119 --> 00:41:33.190
came around the corner at this

00:41:33.200 --> 00:41:36.710
time

00:41:36.720 --> 00:41:38.950
and she saw me on the floor and she felt

00:41:38.960 --> 00:41:40.550
the presence of the Lord so strong in

00:41:40.560 --> 00:41:42.069
the house and she thought I was dying.

00:41:42.079 --> 00:41:43.510
She started screaming. She says, "Jesus,

00:41:43.520 --> 00:41:46.069
don't take him. Don't take him. I need

00:41:46.079 --> 00:41:48.630
my husband. I can't do this on my

00:41:48.630 --> 00:41:48.640
own."She

00:41:48.640 --> 00:41:50.710
goes, "Is he dying? Are you

00:41:50.710 --> 00:41:50.720
dying?"And

00:41:50.720 --> 00:41:52.390
she started yelling. I said,

00:41:52.400 --> 00:41:54.470
"Jesus is here, honey."She says, "I

00:41:54.480 --> 00:41:56.870
know, I can feel it, but I can't see

00:41:56.880 --> 00:42:00.150
him."And

00:42:00.160 --> 00:42:02.710
I started crying out and he

00:42:02.720 --> 00:42:04.790
ministered to me and he put his hand

00:42:04.800 --> 00:42:08.470
on my head and he blessed me.

00:42:08.480 --> 00:42:10.309
He said, "She'll start to amend from

00:42:10.319 --> 00:42:13.190
this

00:42:13.190 --> 00:42:13.200
hour."And

00:42:13.200 --> 00:42:15.829
I knew it's

00:42:15.839 --> 00:42:18.230
going to be gradual like I've always

00:42:18.240 --> 00:42:20.630
told y'all; a miracle is a miracle even

00:42:20.640 --> 00:42:23.670
if it's not overnight.

00:42:23.680 --> 00:42:25.430
A miracle is a miracle even if it's

00:42:25.440 --> 00:42:27.670
progressive.

00:42:27.680 --> 00:42:31.829
I saw everything

00:42:31.839 --> 00:42:34.630
from that day

00:42:34.630 --> 00:42:34.640
forward—that

00:42:34.640 --> 00:42:36.069
I knew it was going to be a

00:42:36.079 --> 00:42:38.390
journey.

00:42:38.400 --> 00:42:40.550
But Jesus told me, "According to your

00:42:40.560 --> 00:42:42.710
faith, be it done unto you."When I woke

00:42:42.720 --> 00:42:45.030
up the next day, I went over and told my

00:42:45.040 --> 00:42:46.790
grandfather because we lived across the

00:42:46.800 --> 00:42:49.750
street at the time. I said, "Grandpa,

00:42:49.760 --> 00:42:51.829
we had a visitation from

00:42:51.829 --> 00:42:51.839
Jesus."Megan

